![ubiquitin]({{site.url}}/assets/Ubiquitin.png)

Made in Unity, the goal of the protein visualiser was to provide some of the functionalities expected from molecular visualisers such as VMD in a VR environment. Hence the decision was made to use the Unity game engine, which supports VR through the SteamVR package.
![VirtualProtein.gif]({{site.url}}/assets/VirtualProtein1.gif)